      "end": 92.42,
      "text": "나중에 보게 되시면"
    },
    {
      "start": 92.42,
      "end": 94.6,
      "text": "It'll help us understand Paris well."
    },
    {
      "start": 94.94,
      "end": 96.66,
      "text": "And prevent future floods."
    },
    {
      "start": 96.9,
      "end": 97.4,
      "text": "그럼요."
    },
    {
      "start": 97.4,
      "end": 99.84,
      "text": "There's never been a flood like that, I think, after then."
    },
    {
      "start": 99.9,
      "end": 104.72,
      "text": "So now they know how to drain the water from the Seine Gang."
    },
    {
      "start": 104.92,
      "end": 105.28,
      "text": "그럼요."
    },
    {
      "start": 105.28,
      "end": 109.62,
      "text": "자, 이제 이 대홍수에 이어서 지금 이 영화 속에서는"
    },
    {
      "start": 109.62,
      "end": 112.1,
      "text": "플립 몬스터까지 출연을 한 상황이잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 112.6,
      "end": 113.76,
      "text": "오늘도 기대됩니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 114.1,
      "end": 115.08,
      "text": "오늘 장면 듣고 오시죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 115.08,
      "end": 118.16,
      "text": "Uh, Commissioner, how do you propose to kill it?"
    },
    {
      "start": 118.48,
      "end": 118.9,
      "text": "Why?"
    },
    {
      "start": 119.04,
      "end": 120.02,
      "text": "With water."
    },
    {
      "start": 120.46,
      "end": 123.18,
      "text": "See, fleas cannot live in water."
    },
    {
      "start": 123.42,
      "end": 125.6,
      "text": "And at the moment, as fate would have it,"
    },
    {
      "start": 125.84,
      "end": 128.02,
      "text": "Paris is full of water."
    },
    {
      "start": 128.38,
      "end": 131.74,
      "text": "Which is why I have not moved more aggressively to drain the streets."
    },
    {
      "start": 132.22,
      "end": 134.84,
      "text": "Water is my weapon of choice."
    },
    {
      "start": 135.18,
      "end": 138.16,
      "text": "When I find the beast, I will take it and drown it."
    },
    {
      "start": 138.16,
      "end": 141.32,
      "text": "Oh, 이제 the Commissioner 있잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 141.48,
      "end": 143.74,
      "text": "May not라는 그 서장이"
    },
    {
      "start": 143.74,
      "end": 145.36,
      "text": "We're starting to move."
    },
    {
      "start": 145.88,
      "end": 148.48,
      "text": "본격적으로 뭔가 일을 행하려고 합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 148.72,
      "end": 150.16,
      "text": "He's gonna get that flea."
    },
    {
      "start": 150.3,
      "end": 151.68,
      "text": "He's gonna kill that flea."
    },
    {
      "start": 151.8,
      "end": 154.98,
      "text": "예, 자, 그 전에 이제 기자회견을 열었는데요."
    },
    {
      "start": 155.88,
      "end": 159.68,
      "text": "보니까 he instigated all the crowd around."
    },
    {
      "start": 160.0,
      "end": 162.52,
      "text": "분위기를 막 부추기는 그런 느낌이 들었어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 162.68,
      "end": 164.2,
      "text": "Yeah, he's really riling them up."
    },
    {
      "start": 164.2,
      "end": 167.92,
      "text": "He's making them angry and eager."
    },
    {
      "start": 168.2,
      "end": 169.72,
      "text": "to catch this flea."
    },
    {
      "start": 169.84,
      "end": 170.12,
      "text": "Right."
    },
    {
      "start": 170.12,
      "end": 171.54,
      "text": "I mean, nobody knows the flea."
    },
    {
      "start": 171.64,
      "end": 172.08,
      "text": "그러니까요."
    },
    {
      "start": 172.1,
      "end": 174.06,
      "text": "They just have heard bad rumors about it."
    },
    {
      "start": 174.16,
      "end": 176.02,
      "text": "소문만 들은 사람들인데도"
    },
    {
      "start": 176.02,
      "end": 177.94,
      "text": "이 서장의 연설을 들으면서"
    },
    {
      "start": 177.94,
      "end": 180.06,
      "text": "굉장히 설득을 당하고"
    },
    {
      "start": 180.06,
      "end": 183.0,
      "text": "거의 엄청 공감을 하는 것 같은 느낌이 들었습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 183.38,
      "end": 185.42,
      "text": "And actually, this is a great distraction"
    },
    {
      "start": 185.42,
      "end": 188.62,
      "text": "for the mayor, for the people."
    },
    {
      "start": 188.96,
      "end": 192.0,
      "text": "The mayor is using this monster as a distraction"
    },
    {
      "start": 192.0,
      "end": 195.44,
      "text": "because he's not doing a good job of handling this flood."
    },
    {
      "start": 195.6,
      "end": 197.62,
      "text": "So he's like, we're gonna use the water"
    },
    {
      "start": 197.62,
      "end": 199.48,
      "text": "to drown the flea"
    },
    {
      "start": 199.48,
      "end": 201.8,
      "text": "and everybody will get distracted"
    },
    {
      "start": 201.8,
      "end": 203.26,
      "text": "from the main problem,"
    },
    {
      "start": 203.4,
      "end": 205.0,
      "text": "which is Paris is underwater."
    },
    {
      "start": 205.0,
      "end": 207.04,
      "text": "아, 주객 전도가 된 것 같은 사람입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 207.04,
      "end": 207.84,
      "text": "바로 주객 전도."
    },
    {
      "start": 208.04,
      "end": 208.28,
      "text": "그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 208.68,
      "end": 209.32,
      "text": "속임수."
    },
    {
      "start": 209.58,
      "end": 213.94,
      "text": "나름 이 속임수의 전략을 잘 짜는 사람인 것 같습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 214.62,
      "end": 217.08,
      "text": "그리고 he already knew the monster's weak point."
    },
    {
      "start": 217.42,
