    },
    {
      "start": 217.74,
      "end": 220.32,
      "text": "Yeah, fleas are really hard to kill."
    },
    {
      "start": 220.6,
      "end": 221.94,
      "text": "I know from personal experience,"
    },
    {
      "start": 222.44,
      "end": 225.66,
      "text": "they were on my dog for so many fleas."
    },
    {
      "start": 225.66,
      "end": 225.96,
      "text": "어륵이요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 226.12,
      "end": 228.84,
      "text": "When I was little, my dog always had fleas."
    },
    {
      "start": 229.0,
      "end": 230.94,
      "text": "And the only way to kill them effectively"
    },
    {
      "start": 230.94,
      "end": 234.6,
      "text": "was to give the dog a really long hot bath"
    },
    {
      "start": 234.6,
      "end": 238.28,
      "text": "and shampoo and that would take care of the fleas."
    },
    {
      "start": 238.46,
      "end": 240.14,
      "text": "그래서 강아지는 좋아했나요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 240.54,
      "end": 242.36,
      "text": "우리 강아지 싫어했어요, 사실."
    },
    {
      "start": 242.66,
      "end": 243.36,
      "text": "목욕 싫어했어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 243.5,
      "end": 245.58,
      "text": "아, 미지근한 물도 아니고"
    },
    {
      "start": 245.58,
      "end": 249.48,
      "text": "약간 hot water에다가 오랫동안 불려야지 떨어지는군요."
    },
    {
      "start": 249.62,
      "end": 252.06,
      "text": "Not too hot, but like pretty hot"
    },
    {
      "start": 252.06,
      "end": 253.42,
      "text": "and then you have to keep scrubbing them"
    },
    {
      "start": 253.42,
      "end": 254.8,
      "text": "with this flea shampoo."
    },
    {
      "start": 255.18,
      "end": 256.22,
      "text": "마사지가 되네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 256.6,
      "end": 258.42,
      "text": "Yeah, special 벼룩용 샴푸 있어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 258.42,
      "end": 261.32,
      "text": "네, 아, 그런 경험이 있으시네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 261.94,
      "end": 263.92,
      "text": "그럼 일단 표현들 점검을 해볼게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 264.98,
      "end": 266.34,
      "text": "As fate would have it."
    },
    {
      "start": 266.5,
      "end": 268.5,
      "text": "As fate would have it."
    },
    {
      "start": 268.66,
      "end": 270.08,
      "text": "라는 표현이 먼저 들렸는데요."
    },
    {
      "start": 270.64,
      "end": 274.3,
      "text": "이게 운 나쁘게도 운명으로 운이 안 좋게도"
    },
    {
      "start": 274.3,
      "end": 277.28,
      "text": "안 됐지만 공교롭게도 라는 의미입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 277.34,
      "end": 278.38,
      "text": "엄청 해석이 많네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 278.78,
      "end": 280.58,
      "text": "네, 다양한 해석을 해드렸어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 280.66,
      "end": 281.96,
      "text": "As fate would have it."
    },
    {
      "start": 282.04,
      "end": 284.04,
      "text": "It's a very nice expression."
    },
    {
      "start": 284.44,
      "end": 285.22,
      "text": "A sophisticated."
    },
    {
      "start": 286.84,
      "end": 287.86,
      "text": "Drain the streets."
    },
    {
      "start": 287.86,
      "end": 289.44,
      "text": "Drain the streets."
    },
    {
      "start": 289.64,
      "end": 290.58,
      "text": "라는 거는 이제"
    },
    {
      "start": 290.58,
      "end": 292.08,
      "text": "street는 거리잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 292.32,
      "end": 295.04,
      "text": "거리에 물을 빼다 라는 의미였습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 295.92,
      "end": 297.0,
      "text": "Weapon of choice."
    },
    {
      "start": 297.14,
      "end": 298.34,
      "text": "Weapon of choice."
    },
    {
      "start": 298.36,
      "end": 301.6,
      "text": "I think I've heard this in the James Bond 007 movies."
    },
    {
      "start": 301.76,
      "end": 303.04,
      "text": "오, 그러네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 303.08,
      "end": 303.86,
      "text": "Weapon of choice."
    },
    {
      "start": 304.14,
      "end": 305.14,
      "text": "The golden gun."
    },
    {
      "start": 305.36,
      "end": 305.78,
      "text": "그랬나요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 305.94,
      "end": 307.12,
      "text": "기억이 가물가물하네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 307.32,
      "end": 308.24,
      "text": "Weapon of choice."
    },
    {
      "start": 308.54,
      "end": 310.84,
      "text": "게임하는 사람들 많이 들어봤을 것 같다."
    },
    {
      "start": 310.86,
      "end": 311.28,
      "text": "그렇군요."
